prodNameC: 威力安TM II T醣化血紅素分析測試
prodNameE: VARIANTTM II TURBO Hemoglobin A1c Program
ingredientsDesc:
270-2401: Elution Buffer A
Three bottles containing 2500 ml of a Bis-Tris/Phosphate buffer, 
pH 6.0. Contains < 0.05% sodium azide as a preservative.
270-2402: Elution Buffer B 
One bottle containing 1500 ml of a Bis-Tris/Phosphate buffer, 
pH 6.7. Contains < 0.05% sodium azide as a preservative.
270-2410: Cartridge Set
Onc cation exchange (2000 test) analytical Cartridge (4.0mm ID x 34.2mm), and five cation exchange (400 tests each) Guard Cartridges (4.6 mm ID x 15.4 mm). Store cartridges at 2-8℃.
270-2409; CD-ROM with VARIANT II TURBO Hemoglobin A1c program parameters.
270-2404: Calibrator/Diluent Set.
One set consisting of three vials of calibrator level 1, three vials of Calibrator 2, and one bottle of Calibrator Diluent. The calibrator vials contain lypholized human red blood cell hemolysate with gentamicin, tobramycin, and EDTA as preservatives,. Reconstituted volume is 7ml per vial. Calibrator Diluent contains 100 ml of deionized water with < 0.05% sodium azide as a preservative.
270-2413: W
